Used to enter a specific Locale on which to perform an Action, such as Add Word. The locale used on the device is selecting using the [UI Manager](../uimgr/#set-current-locale). 

**Parm value input rules**:

* A string from 2-10 characters
* Must correspond to a locale installed on the device 
